>Dr Kyle</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">: It might be worth stress</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">ing</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> that </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">the extraordinary thing about </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">the 1,000 apprentices you are taking on at Barclays is </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">that </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">a high degree of them have no qualifications at all.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">The Chairman:</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> It is the best thing.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Dr Kyle</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">: Yes. So these are getting to young people who—</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">The Chairman:</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> That is good.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Dr Kyle</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">: Exactly.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold">Q101 </span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family